      public boolean checkManagerAssigned(Connection connection)
      Searches through employees of teams to see if manager appears, this is so that when assigning managers, appropriate dialog can be displayed asking the user if they are sure that they want to carry out the assignment.
      Returns:
      whether the manager is assigned to a team
